We are going to pay for people stuck in other countries, we are going to pay with more cases coming into Canada from the USA that is basically unnecessary travel. Isn't this simple to stop USA people from coming here unless its trade or business related? I don't like the fact that it seems like Canadian Government is scared of what the Trump government might do in retaliation. Its peoples lives at stake.  Trump or whoever is in charge, this is not important at this point. I hope people in the USA are smart enough to stay away in spite of this open boarder. We don't want them here.
